\begin_layout Standard
Consider now the discrete time series 
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{X}=\left(\boldsymbol{x}_{1},\boldsymbol{x}_{2},...,\boldsymbol{x}_{N}\right)$
\end_inset

, consisting of 
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

